description: Record to support submission of GeneRIFs for a gene not in Gene (Bacillus Delbrucki; Bacillus acidificans longissimus; Bacterium delbrucki; Lactobacillus delbrucki; Lactobacterium delbrucki; Plocamobacterium delbrucki; Thermobacterium cereale; Ulvina delbrucki.  Use when strain, subtype, isolate, etc. is unspecified, or when different from all specified ones in Gene.).
